node.text:
It is the stuff of daydreams: Visiting the nearest car dealer and putting the money for your favourite sports car on the table – in cash. AMG fan Debra Bennett, who craved a little more thrill after a demanding career, did just that. In the new episode of AMG Uncovered, we learn why it was so appealing to her to race her dream car across the asphalt.

#AMGUncovered #MercedesAMG #PerformanceLuxury #NewLuxury #CarofInstagram

In our new episode of AMG Uncovered, Jess explains how important it was to overcome the common stereotypes in order to unlock her true self.

Tech talk with Phillipp Schiemer and Jochen Hermann: Mercedes-AMG is combining superior performance and impressive driving dynamics with maximum efficiency through the future electrification of our drivetrains. The development of electrified drive concepts are realized in cooperation with the Formula 1 experts at Mercedes-AMG High Performance Powertrains (HPP) and @mercedesamgf1. This transfer of knowledge helps to make fascinating AMG models, such as the Mercedes-AMG Project ONE hypercar, possible.
 
With more electrified road models debuting later this year, there is plenty to look forward to in the future of Driving Performance!

Our Mercedes-AMG Customer Racing Teams celebrated an overall and a class win in the two races of the @gtworldchallengeeurope last weekend. 
 
After finishing in P2 in the first race, @maroengel and @lucastolz of the #6 Mercedes-AMG Team @toksportwrt took victory in the second race, whilst the #7 Toksport WRT with drivers @juusopuhakka and @oscartunjo secured a class win in the Silver Cup in Race 2.
 
In total, the eight Mercedes-AMG GT3s secured three overall podiums and five class podiums at @brandshatchofficial. 🏆

The fifth and final Sprint Cup event of the 2021 season will be held at @circuitvalencia  on 25 – 26 September.

node.text:
Crazy Race Day at the #BelgianGP! 😮 After more than three hours of delay, the race was red flagged due to bad weather conditions. Having completed a few laps, @mercedesamgf1 will receive half the points of a full race.
Keeping their starting positions, it's P3 for @lewishamilton and P12 for @valtteribottas.

#WeLivePerformance @mercedesamgmotorsport
